snippet.title: Amber Heard Rejected Elon Musk For ‘a Long Time’ | Splash News TV
snippet.description:
Amber Heard rejected Elon Musk's first attempts to date her for a "long time." Wonder how many times he had to ask… A billion?

Subscribe now for the latest Daily Hollywood Celebrity Splash TV News: https://goo.gl/JaLP0U

Best Daily Splash News Daily Celebrity Playlist: https://goo.gl/QsxT0r

So everyone knows Amber Heard and Elon Musk are getting serious after officially announcing that they’re dating.

But according to Us Magazine, it took the billionaire Tesla CEO a long time before she was willing to take him up on a date. 

In fact, Elon reportedly first met Amber in 2013 when they were both respectfully married to other people, but Us Weekly reports, “Elon has been pursuing Amber, but she wouldn’t go out with him for a long time.” 

Hmm… Then reports said, “She finally gave in… He even got her a Tesla.” 

Well, yeah. If Amber Heard was dating a franchise owner of a Pizza Hut, we’d suspect that he’d bring her a pizza home every now and again too, so that only makes sense. Luckily though, her man owns a state of the art electric car company… Nice! 

We wonder how many times Elon had to ask Amber out before she said yes though… Maybe, a billion?
